21 nonclassified personnel shall be the lesser of Twenty-five Thousand
22 Dollars ($25,000.00) or one-half (1/2) of the member's final average
23 salary used in computing retirement benefits unless the earnings
24 limitation allowed by the Social Security Administration would be
